# Fork-Only Git Operations

- Push branches only to `bkarciauskas/food-delivery-multivendor` via the `origin` remote.
- Create pull requests with both the head branch and base branch on `bkarciauskas/food-delivery-multivendor`.
- Never push to or create pull requests against `enatega/food-delivery-multivendor` or the `upstream` remote.
- Before creating a pull request, verify its destination repository explicitly.
- If the intended fork or remote is ambiguous, ask before pushing or creating the pull request.
